    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Motionmelody</strong> is an experimental musical bullet-hell featuring a carefully picked collection of songs by both international and niche musicians, complemented by its fully-featured Level Editor, you will never run out of levels to play! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175480/extras/009359b4da4b24df501816ff02abe276.poster.avif?t=1736843087\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175480/extras/009359b4da4b24df501816ff02abe276.webm?t=1736843087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175480/extras/009359b4da4b24df501816ff02abe276.mp4?t=1736843087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Completely free! No microtransactions, ads, or DLC.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Carefully created level editor that enables users to create their own levels, challenges, or whatever else, to whatever music they wish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple unique official levels to play with awesome soundtracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A handful of game-modes to play in, always keep a lookout for them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use practice mode to sharpen your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with a mouse, keyboard, or a game-pad.</p></li></ul>",
